    "name": "Neighbors",
    "steam_appid": 3030680,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030680/extras/eee4ab6aff83d3de3edfdc52e153c337.avif?t=1743466244\" width=594 height=69 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你决定在迷人的小镇西耶拉开始新的生活。带着你的行李和手机，踏上这段令人兴奋的冒险之旅。成为你想成为的人，遇见独特的个性，探索并与周围的世界建立深厚的联系。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030680/extras/2d40c8582a30b00c38e8689d62128699.avif?t=1743466244\" width=616 height=342 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索、收集、装饰、社交、放松，并揭开谜团。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030680/extras/14c158e88c3c9f2c054dde779d905357.avif?t=1743466244\" width=594 height=69 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>塑造你的命运</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索一个充满奇迹和秘密的世界，等待你去发现。选择你的生活方式：专注于农业、在当地的面包店工作，或者寻找其他的方式。与任何你选择的人一起，以你自己的节奏和方式建立你的生活。掌控权在你手中！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030680/extras/fe9c82764b161490455b638e76134f75.poster.avif?t=1743466244\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030680/extras/fe9c82764b161490455b638e76134f75.webm?t=1743466244\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030680/extras/fe9c82764b161490455b638e76134f75.mp4?t=1743466244\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>成为你想成为的人</strong><br>通过丰富的体型、服装和配饰自定义你的外观。找到你独特的风格，以你喜欢的方式表达自己。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>与多样化的人物建立联系</strong><br>了解你的邻居和小镇居民。建立友谊，与任何你喜欢的人约会，聊天并发现他们的兴趣，并用他们喜欢的礼物给他们惊喜。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030680/extras/d15ba255d412ef713f90b285e3e1c498.avif?t=1743466244\" width=616 height=374 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>找到你的另一半</strong>发展浪漫关系，赢得你的特别之人，当你准备好时，一起在西耶拉踏上令人兴奋的旅程。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>把你的房子变成一个家</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >按照你的喜好装饰和重新设计你的公寓。购买新家具，改变地板和墙壁。邀请你的邻居们来举办一场最棒的派对。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030680/extras/95896033f87b289405dedf9659bcc80f.poster.avif?t=1743466244\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030680/extras/95896033f87b289405dedf9659bcc80f.webm?t=1743466244\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030680/extras/95896033f87b289405dedf9659bcc80f.mp4?t=1743466244\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>揭开谜团</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >奇怪的事件正在打扰你邻居们的安宁。调查并找出发生了什么。你会独自面对这些谜团吗？你会寻求帮助吗？还是选择避开它们？选择权在你手中！</p></li></ul>",
